{"tid":1643991,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【被DQ】2019花式足球香港冠軍港將黎俊賢因在IG上發表FREE HK取消資格","createTime":"2019-10-10T11:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:48:53.000Z","uid":44930,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a92470c888f67d560fa0278aba8c3cb538737cb5","tid":1643991,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQfUG2T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQfUG2T.jpg&h=a6d0a716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亞錦賽主辦方負責人日前通知港將施寶盛，有人匿名舉報黎俊賢的帖文，暗示希望後者能退賽，甚或取消其參賽資格。事件發酵一日後，亞錦賽組委會發出聲明，指大會「堅決捍衛一個中國原則、堅決擁護祖國統一、堅決維護國家主權及領土完整、堅決反對任何企圖分裂國家的言論和行為」，並由即日起對發表涉港、涉台不當言論的參賽選手予以禁賽處罰。雖然聲明未有點名指選手誰屬，但黎俊賢指自己已收到通知被取消參賽資格。這是他繼2017年接受訪問談及回歸20年的感受後，第2次因類似原因被禁賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iumgVoN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiumgVoN.png&h=69a685c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時人ig，係香港人嘅去支持下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yin_freestyle/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyin_freestyle%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=92860109\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yin_freestyle/?hl=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"a86b878cbdbd6f497c83fa07af1df9e179f89cb9","tid":1643991,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffacfbf550ad9d9d7c5268499982f0c5fec4a15","tid":1643991,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676f5c51d4dfbd68cd01b3ca3e4853960fc7dbf3","tid":1643991,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72c5d87de57e9dab3dd5ca7e250c2649fddc921